{"tid":402853,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（2017試食）東海堂抹茶流心月餅","createTime":"2017-09-16T17:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T12:55:09.000Z","uid":67171,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"38a61107be1ced5f635ae7ea78e1163f5210937a","tid":402853,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"今年東海堂出左抹茶流心月餅<br />\n話北海道3.6牛乳做餡 加埋小山園若竹個隻等級嘅抹茶流心<br />\n聽落好高級 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7月尾拿拿聲就訂左<br />\n終於到9月我就去左拎<br />\n哇 間鋪寫住賣哂喎<br />\n以為自己好醒一早訂左好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到屋屋企梗係拿拿聲開黎食啦<br />\n個盒好高級咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一切開 哇 真係流架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咦<br />\n但食落無抹茶味嘅<br />\n再咬入d<br />\n哇屌你個餡係杏霜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n說好的3.6牛乳呢？<br />\n全家人都係咬左1或2啖就掉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係第一次食咁難食嘅月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議大家未開就送禮<br />\n未拎卷就轉手<br />\n開左唔緊要 捐俾想食嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係你會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018a4a9a704793ff84a2ceabe86310d6d5147631","tid":402853,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"無人食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bea9d3e25d43c3850e6eb727723a76205eb1bab","tid":402853,"uid":82829,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"點解你會對呢啲嘢有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗個啲無腦港女仲會係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615934a1a74cf92ad206c2f6f9e52900053fbb79","tid":402853,"uid":53254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"以為打手文<br />\n最後plot twist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8382a6514675f317837c2748786781daa8edd1","tid":402853,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T19:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你會對呢啲嘢有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗個啲無腦港女仲會係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你對咩月餅有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b290cb91cb1c95014cae54db64590568ea8cdf4","tid":402853,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T19:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為打手文<br />\n最後plot twist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小妹唔做打手的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲d再分享下其他野食"},{"pid":"c9bee329d8990b9e1921ea0d3622f87be04c6806","tid":402853,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T19:05:01.000Z","msg":"想補充返 自己亂整綠茶月餅都好食過佢好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"