":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dwe24yp1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdwe24yp1&h=10264b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌, 裏面個餡同流心餡冇乜味, 就連個皮都咁撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 有冇人食過n年前既冰燒月? <br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uWUdOJbDe88/UoodL-va7RI/AAAAAAAAdhw/EXeGJ6Ebujc/s1600/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-uWUdOJbDe88%2FUoodL-va7RI%2FAAAAAAAAdhw%2FEXeGJ6Ebujc%2Fs1600%2F2.jpg&h=8ba102c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b1c4877c621ce90f06b75fe18f94e1bfb9ba2b3","tid":402853,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇個包裝好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個廣告仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}